address1: 89 Main Road, Diep River, Tramway Villiage

partnerDetails.about: Plumstead Electrical, established in 1968 by Sandy Gold, expanded their business in 2004 to service Cape Town’s Northern Suburbs when Okavango Electrical Wholesalers and Lighting was opened. General Manager and Director, Morne Vermeulen, runs the electrical wholesale and lighting division at Okavango Electrical alongside brothers Bruce and Glenn Gold, based at Plumstead Electrical Wholesalers.
